descriptions.direction: Located in Vakkaru, Vakkaru Maldives is on a private beach. Thulhaadho Beach is another place to visit that comes recommended. Discover the area's water adventures with windsurfing nearby, or enjoy the great outdoors with hiking/biking trails.
descriptions.general: Vakkaru Maldives is located in Baa Atoll, Maldives. The nearby points of interest are The Organic Farm, Sand Boutique, Isoleta, Onu, Parrotfish Club, Vakkru, Sports Field and Splash. The closest airport to Vakkaru Maldives is Ifuru Airport (IFU) at 64km. Facilities and servicesde 24-hour reception, air conditioning, babysitting services (extra charge), a bar (extra charge), a breakfast room (extra charge), a café (extra charge), a children's play area, a children's pool, concierge facilities, gym/fitness facilities, ironing facilities, laundry facilities (extra charge), a lounge, multilingual staff, a pool bar (extra charge), a restaurant (extra charge), a sauna, shuttle services, spa facilities, a swimming pool, wheelchair access, and Wi-Fi access. Room features include air conditioning, a balcony/terrace, a bathrobe, cable/satellite TV, cleaning/housekeeping, a coffee/tea maker, connecting rooms available (extra charge), cots on request, a desk, a hairdryer, a living room, a mini bar/fridge (extra charge), a private pool (extra charge), room service (extra charge), a safe box, a shower, a telephone, toiletries provided, towels provided, and Wi-Fi access. Address: Level 2, Office of H. Nooranifehi, Abadhaffehi Magu, MALE 20041 Maldives
